Agile
Pods , small team , autonomous 
iterative approach , typically 2 weeks iteration

pods : 5-9 people , product owner . Scrum master . pod member reports to chapter lead
crew : collection 5-10 pods , senior product and delvy manager
Chapter : multiple crews , chapeter lead reports to crew or stream lead
stream : e.g. stream technical lead, stream product lead 
guild : employees with same skills

crew big room review 3 times a quarter  set pods OKRs
poclac event 5 times a quarter , pod performance

stories are 2 days in length

OKR : Goals against objectives , outcome focussed , client focussed , 3 to 5 objectives , quarterly
KPI : overall health of team , output focussed

Agile way of working instead of big bang release
